<NEW>

SABERBACK seemed to be paying little attention to NIGHTLIGHT at the
moment as he continued to talk on the radio. "What do you mean that
you can't get one open?" He said into his radio. "There is a secondary
portal built into the system in there."

There was a pause as SABERBACK walked in silence, the SHARKTICONS
continuing to push NIGHTLIGHT along, snickering while they watched
her. They had no idea of the thoughts she had in her head, but they
did seem to enjoy the guilt, anger and fear she was projecting.

"Excellent." SABERBACK said into his radio. "Have it ready when we
arrive." SABERBACK's pace picked up once again.

(TAG)

- Preston
